  "remarks": "GBi.006 Designation: a) Lieutenant-colonel b) Head of Intelligence. Passport no: DA0001564, issued on 30 Nov. 2005, issued in Guinea-Bissau (Expiration date 15 May 2011). Other information: Na Bidon was listed on 18 Jul. 2012 pursuant to paragraph 4 of resolution 2048 (2012) as “Member of the “Military Command” which has assumed responsibility for the coup d'état of 12 April 2012.” Parentage: “Nabidom”.; Listing: Listed by 2048 Committee on 18 Jul. 2012",
